- Yes.

112
00:13:12,033 --> 00:13:15,953
Sure.
What's your name?

113
00:13:16,273 --> 00:13:17,833
Shivam.
- Shivam, right.

114
00:13:31,153 --> 00:13:32,113
Isn't he so cool?

115
00:13:34,553 --> 00:13:37,433
Shivam, I've to talk
to you about something.

116
00:13:37,873 --> 00:13:42,313
Hey, Shiva! Is that your dad?

117
00:13:43,553 --> 00:13:45,273
Say 'Hi' to him.

118
00:13:58,193 --> 00:14:01,513
Dad, would it be okay if my friend
came with us to Mussoorie?

119
00:14:01,833 --> 00:14:05,433
Which friend?
T-that boy?

120
00:14:05,713 --> 00:14:07,913
I offered the ride.

121
00:14:08,753 --> 00:14:10,433
