to school for a reason.

127
00:14:25,513 --> 00:14:28,793
I've to talk to you.
Come. Come and sit in the car.

128
00:14:29,433 --> 00:14:30,793
You always have your way.

129
00:14:42,913 --> 00:14:44,073
We'll go to grandma's.

130
00:14:45,673 --> 00:14:46,993
