146
00:15:40,640 --> 00:15:42,560
Darn! We forgot our seat belts.

147
00:15:42,840 --> 00:15:44,000
Don't tell mom.
She is wild.

148
00:15:44,080 --> 00:15:45,320
Just wait I'll tell you.

149
00:15:46,023 --> 00:15:48,023
